descriptionHtml:
Welcome to Hit Master! is a Humble and amusing game.
Guide and master the blade by moving softly and gently with your touch.
Everything can be moved you need to be careful to avoid black items
You can make an army with assistant blades !

Infinity white Bubbles!
Needs accuracy in movement!
Collect stars as many you can!
Each level has lots of stars to collect!
Limitless time!
Sleep mode game!

✔ One-Touch control
✔ Playing without Wi-Fi- offline
✔ Made with Unity

Easy to learn but hard to control. Ready to roll the blade? Download now!
Always improving and developing to bring you fun!
